    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Professors with the highest ranking position on the staff of a university or college, having full rank and privliges, and in a position higher than associate professors or assistant professors.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
